asset.hookText: For a hands-and-knees clean, there's nothing better -- and easier --than the Hoover FloorMate. It washes and dries all the bare floors in your home, from tile to hardwood to laminate and even grout. We've created this simple video to help you out when your FloorMate won't dispense solution, or when it stops spraying when you squeeze the trigger.
